snippet.title: Seven Beats Music
snippet.description:
• Seven Beats Music • 

One of the best labels you can bump into. Levitating between trip-hop & deep house, organic & oriental sound, here you'll find various selection of seamlessly mixed DJ sets, magical Spiritual Journey mixes and eclectic Coffeeshop Selections.

Enjoy the vibe!

Contact: sevenbeatslabel@gmail.com
